<h4 id="centroid">Centroid</h4>
<p>ì´ë¯¸ì§€ ë‚´ì˜ objectì˜ ìœ„ì¹˜ê°€ ê³µê°„ ìœ„ì¹˜ì— ì˜í•´ ì •í•´ì§„ë‹¤.</p>

<p>Center of area(centroid, center of mass): First order moment</p>

<ul>
  <li>\(\bar{x} = {\sum_i^n \sum_j^m {jB[i,j]} \over A}\) (objectì˜ pixelê°„ì— j ì¢Œí‘œì˜ í‰ê· )</li>
  <li>
    <p>\(\bar{y} = {\sum_i^n \sum_j^m {iB[i,j]} \over A}\) (objectì˜ pixelê°„ì— i ì¢Œí‘œì˜ í‰ê· )</p>
  </li>
  <li>intensity centroid</li>
  <li>binary imageì˜ ê¸°í•˜í•™ì  ì¤‘ì‹¬</li>
  <li>CentroidëŠ” ë¶„ì„ê³¼ ë§¤ì¹­ì—ì„œ interesting pointê°€ ë  ìˆ˜ ìˆë‹¤.</li>
